<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Notification - Heartly</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a6f 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f8f9ff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .alert {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .info-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: white;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff6b6b;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border: 1px solid #b3d9ff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #ff5252;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üîê Password Reset Notification</h1>
        <p>Your account password has been reset</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Security Alert</h2>
        
        <div class="alert">
            <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Your password has been reset</h3>
            <p>An administrator has reset your password for security reasons.</p>
        </div>

        <p>Hello,</p>
        
        <p>This is to notify you that your password for your Heartly account has been reset by an administrator. Here are the details:</p>

        <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Reset Time:</strong> {{resetTime}}
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Reset By:</strong> System Administrator
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
            <h3>üõ°Ô∏è What happens next:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>You will receive a separate email with your temporary password</li>
                <li>Your temporary password will expire in 24 hours</li>
                <li>You must set a new password on your first login</li>
                <li>All existing sessions have been terminated for security</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn">Go to Login Page</a>
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
            <h3>üö® Didn't request this reset?</h3>
            <p>If you didn't request this password reset or have concerns about your account security:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Contact your facility administrator immediately</li>
                <li>Do not use the temporary password if provided</li>
                <li>Report this as a potential security incident</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h3>Security Best Practices:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Never share your login credentials with others</li>
            <li>Use a unique, strong password for your Heartly account</li>
            <li>Log out completely when using shared computers</li>
            <li>Report any suspicious account activity immediately</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent from Heartly - Healthcare Facility Management System</p>
        <p>This is an automated security notification, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Heartly. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>